{"type": "article", "id": 19476, "title": "圣诞树灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-22T07:40:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000411EQRbxVNwcD1ygKG3.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t巴西的设计工作室 Ambos 擅长将人的行为和灯光做艺术上的联系，设计带有实验性质的作品。这棵圣诞树上布置了圆形的灯泡，在条形的枝叶上连接了特殊的电线，产生出明暗交替的效果。整棵树中像是有无数闪烁的萤火虫在莹莹晃动，可以成为未来节日装点时的发展方向，<a href=\"http://vimeo.com/148455424\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看详细视频。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145947fogpZDGK7RnXHiax.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"343\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.57166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145948jY9dEeW7Aq0I4Xay.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"591\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.54722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145949kvDZx7AdzplaPtJ2.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145953l3sMiHzejJgdx2oh.gif\" width=\"540\" height=\"304\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}